verbose_text: It was found that all three major ER stress mediated signaling pathways were involved in the ER stress mediated overproductions of MUC5AC and MUC5B and that the three pathways were involved individually in the up-regulations of MUC5AC and MUC5B in human airway epithelial cells.
evidence: ER stress-mediated overproductions of MUC5AC and MUC5B
